@startuml
[*] --> ActiveTeacher
ActiveTeacher --> ActiveTeacher : sysadmin updates profile
ActiveTeacher --> InactiveTeacher : admin disables account
InactiveTeacher --> ActiveTeacher : admin re-enables account
ActiveTeacher --> AdminRole : promote role
AdminRole --> ActiveTeacher : demote role
ActiveTeacher --> DiscordBotConfigured : sysadmin saves bot credential
DiscordBotConfigured --> DiscordBotHealthy : health worker succeeds
DiscordBotConfigured --> DiscordBotUnhealthy : health worker fails
DiscordBotUnhealthy --> DiscordBotConfigured : credential updated
ActiveTeacher --> [*]
InactiveTeacher --> [*]
@enduml
